{"tid":2165994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【灣仔一女子被多名便衣警拉上七人車】","createTime":"2020-08-20T07:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T07:32:23.000Z","uid":146038,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"82ff18d28a5434f6a39b0126d63719a7b94b4df0","tid":2165994,"uid":146038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:08:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3376379062447690\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F3376379062447690&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRuffUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=fbf77ad4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3376379062447690</a><br />\n<br />\n有讀者向《立場新聞》提供影片及表示，今早（20 日）9 時許，於灣仔柯布連道與謝斐道交界天橋底，一名女子遭 5 至 8 名便衣拉上一輛黑色 7 人車。讀者提供的影片顯示被押上車的女子持續大叫，有便衣向車內說「我已經拘捕咗你」。現場似乎有市民上前詢問發生何事，便衣回答指「我哋已經拘捕咗佢」，之後黑色 7 人車就駛走。<br />\n《立場新聞》根據讀者提供的車牌資料查詢，系統表示車牌「已預留政府使用」。《立場》已向警察公共關係科查詢事件，暫時未有回覆。"},{"pid":"664f990b63c0fa0d2347d2c17d13545f209f4d9a","tid":2165994,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"4ba21426f894b804df459f4ced7c83435b71ceb4","tid":2165994,"uid":313974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:14:04.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f22e1186555462159fb7fdebb8f102713c8d546","tid":2165994,"uid":160251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:15:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f40dff0491d1bca2b266ddc35651d3ac36b83ca1","tid":2165994,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98728e6b032e547b7b5f232d551db3597e05b738","tid":2165994,"uid":19528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl